race.comment: Competitive. ZELGARIA (4) has been racing in stronger grade. Was cruelled by the 11 gate at Doomben but missed by 2L there prior and that stacks right up for this. 2x winning rider Mallyon is back on replacing the 3kg apprentice. TOWN CRIER (3) missed a lip in the race won by MINTAKA LAD. Will lead or box seat from the inside barrier and also has decent claims. MINTAKA LAD (1) did a good job winning that contest after settling back and covering ground. He's capable of sitting closer and has a 3kg claimer aboard for this.Will get very chance again. MISHANI RENEGADE (2) seeks the hat trick. This is tougher but winning rider Ben Thompson is back on replacing the apprentice. He has scope for more improvement.
